 Man (song)|Rocket Man]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| 11\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| \"[[Hard Luck Woman]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| Eliminated\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| Laci Kaye Booth\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| 2\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| \"[[The House That Built Me]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| 7\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| \"[[Saturday Night's Alright for Fighting]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| 12\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| \"[[Dreams (Fleetwood Mac song)|Dreams]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| Eliminated\n|-\n| [[Alejandro Aranda]]\n| 3\n| \"[[No Woman No Cry]]\"\n| 8<br />\n| \"[[Sorry Seems to Be the Hardest Word]]\"\n| 15\n| \"Blesser\" {{small|(original song)}}\n| style=\"background:#FDFC8F;\"| Safe\n|-\n| [[Laine Hardy]]\n| 4\n| \"[[Can't You See (The Marshall Tucker Band song)|Can't You See]]\"\n| 10\n| \"[[Something About The Way You Look Tonight]]\"\n| 14\n| \"[[Hey Jude]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FDFC8F;\"| Safe\n|-\n| Madison VanDenburg\n| 5\n| \"[[What About Us (Pink song)|What About Us]]\"\n| 9\n| \"[[Your Song]]\"\n| 13\n| \"[[Make You Feel My Love]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FDFC8F;\"| Safe\n|}\n\n===Week 5: Finale (May 19)===\nThis week, the Top 3 performed their two songs, one contestant was eliminated landing in 3rd place, based on the results up to that point. Voting continued for the remaining two contestants and closed after the two finalists sang their last songs.\n\n'''Color key:'''\n{| class=\"toccolours\"style=\"font-size: 90%; white-space: nowrap;\"\n|-\n| style=\"background:tan; border:1px solid black;\"| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n| Contestant finished in 3rd place.\n|-\n| style=\"background:silver; border:1px solid black;\"| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n| Contestant finished as the runner-up.\n|-\n| style=\"background:gold; border:1px solid black;\"| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n| Contestant won the season.\n|}\n{| class=\"w