 Do It]]\"\n|-\n| 19.4\n| Katy Perry and [[Daddy Yankee]]\n| \"[[Con Calma]]\"\n|-\n| 19.5\n| [[Alejandro Aranda]]\n| \"10 Years\" {{small|(original song)}}\n|-\n| 19.6\n| [[Adam Lambert]]\n| \"[[New Eyes (Adam Lambert song)|New Eyes]]\"\n|-\n| 19.7\n| Adam Lambert with Dimitrius Graham\n| \"[[Bohemian Rhapsody]]\"\n|-\n| 19.8\n| [[Dan + Shay]]\n| \"[[Dan + Shay (album)|All To Myself]]\"\n|-\n| 19.9\n| [[Dan + Shay]] with Madison VanDenburg\n| \"[[Speechless (Dan + Shay song)|Speechless]]\"\n|-\n| 19.10\n| Luke Bryan\n| \"[[Luke Bryan#2015\u2013present: Kill the Lights, What Makes You Country and untitled seven studio album|Knockin' Boots]]\"\n|-\n| 19.11\n| Luke Bryan with Laci Kaye Booth\n| \"[[Every Breath You Take]]\"\n|-\n| 19.12\n| [[Jon Pardi]] with [[Laine Hardy]]\n| \"[[Dirt On My Boots]]\" & \"[[Night Shift (Jon Pardi song)|Night Shift]]\"\n|-\n| 19.13\n| Katy Perry with [[Jeremiah Lloyd Harmon]]\n| \"[[Unconditionally]]\"\n|-\n| 19.14\n| [[Weezer]] with Wade Cota\n| \"[[Africa (Toto song)|Africa]]\"\n|-\n| 19.15\n| [[Weezer]]\n| \"[[Everybody Wants to Rule the World]]\"\n|-\n| 19.16\n| [[Weezer]] with Walker Burroughs and Wade Cota\n| \"[[Take On Me]]\"\n|-\n| 19.17\n| [[Kane Brown]]\n| \"[[Good as You (song)|Good as You]]\"\n|-\n| 19.18\n| [[Kane Brown]] with Alyssa Raghu\n| \"[[Lost in the Middle of Nowhere]]\"\n|-\n| 19.19\n| [[Andra Day]] with Shayy\n| \"[[Rise Up (Andra Day song)|Rise Up]]\"\n|-\n| 19.20\n| [[Kool & the Gang]] with Uch\u00e9\n| \"[[Hollywood Swinging]]\"\n|-\n| 19.21\n| [[Kool & the Gang]] with Laci Kaye Booth, Madison VanDenburg and Alyssa Raghu\n| \"[[Ladies' Night (song)|Ladies Night]]\"\n|-\n| 19.22\n| [[Kool & the Gang]] with the Top 10\n| \"[[Celebration (Kool & the Gang song)|Celebration]]\"\n|-\n| 19.23\n| [[Laine Hardy]]\n| \"[[Flame (Laine Hardy song)|Flame]]\" {{small|(original song)}}\n|-\n|}\n\n== Elimination chart ==\n<center>\n'''Color key'''\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" style=\"background:gray; border:1px solid 