ay-final-ratings-march-31-2019/ |title='Good Girls,' 'NCIS: Los Angeles,' and others adjust up: Sunday final ratings |last=Welch |first=Alex |date=April 2, 2019 |website=TV by the Numbers |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402143559/https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/sunday-final-ratings-march-31-2019/ |archive-date=April 2, 2019 |access-date=April 2, 2019}}</ref>\n| dvr8       = 0.4\n| dvrv8      = 1.56\n| total8     = 1.6\n| totalv8    = 8.78<ref name=\"DVR 7, 8\" />\n\n| title9     = Top 20 Solos\n| date9      = April 1, 2019\n| timeslot9  = Monday 8:00 p.m.\n| rs9        = 1.1/5\n| viewers9   = 6.23<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/monday-final-ratings-april-1-2019/ |title='Legends of Tomorrow' adjusts down: Monday final ratings |last=Rejent |first=Joseph |date=April 2, 2019 |website=TV by the Numbers |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402212642/https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/monday-final-ratings-april-1-2019/ |archive-date=April 2, 2019 |access-date=April 2, 2019}}</ref>\n| dvr9       = 0.4\n| dvrv9      = 1.92\n| total9     = 1.5\n| totalv9    = 8.15<ref name=\"DVR 9, 10\">{{Cite web |url=https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-this-is-us-third-season-finale-on-nbc-tops-all-telecasts-in-overall-raw-gains/ |title=Live+7 Weekly Ratings: \u2018This Is Us\u2019 Third Season Finale on NBC Tops All Telecasts in Overall Raw Gains |last=Pucci |first=Douglas |date=April 16, 2019 |website=Programming Insider |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417003757/https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-this-is-us-third-season-finale-on-nbc-tops-all-telecasts-in-overall-raw-gains/ |archive-date=April 17, 2019 |access-date=April 18, 2019}}</ref>\n\n| title10    = All-Star Duets, Part 1\n| date10     = April 7, 2019\n| timeslot10 = Sunday 8:00 p.m.\n| rs10       = 1.0/5\n| viewers10  = 6.12<ref>{{Cite web |url=htt