host/3398073002/ |title='American Idol': Bobby Bones steps in for ailing Ryan Seacrest on Monday's episode |website=USA Today |language=en |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408215556/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2019/04/08/american-idol-ryan-seacrest-sick-bobby-bones-host/3398073002/ |archive-date=2019-04-08 |access-date=2019-04-09}}</ref>\n\n'''Color key:'''\n{| class=\"toccolours\" style=\"font-size: 90%; white-space: nowrap;\"\n|-\n| style=\"background:#B0E0E6; border:1px solid black;\"| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n| Contestant was chosen by the judges to move on to the live shows\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4; border:1px solid black;\"| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n| Contestant was eliminated\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:99%;\"\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:10%;\"| Date of airing\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:4%;\"| Order\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:15%;\"| Contestant\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:18%;\"| Song<ref name=\"DuetsSetList\">{{Cite tweet |number=1114587229429456897 |user=AmericanIdol |title=Get your weekend ALL-STARted with the #IdolDuets lineups! \ud83c\udf1f Watch #AmericanIdol Sunday & Monday 8{{!}}7c on ABC \u2728 |author=American Idol |date=April 6, 2019 |access-date=April 6, 2019 |archive-url=https://archive.is/cvZCT |archive-date=April 6, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:15%;\"| Duet partner<ref name=\"DuetsSetList\" />\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:9%;\" | Result<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://tvline.com/2019/04/07/american-idol-recap-season-17-duets-eliminations-watch-video/ |title=''American Idol'' Recap: Are the Right Seven Singers Going Live? Watch the Best All-Star Duets and Weigh In |last=Swift |first=Andy |date=April 7, 2019 |website=[[TV Line]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408040811/https://tvline.com/2019/04/07/american-idol-recap-season-17-duets-eliminations-watch-video/ |ar