 Story]]''\n| style=\"background:#FDFC8F;\"| Safe\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| 6\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| Dimitrius Graham\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| \"[[You'll Be in My Heart]]\"\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| ''[[Tarzan (1999 film)|Tarzan]]''\n| style=\"background:#FF91A4;\"| Eliminated\n|-\n| 7\n| Walker Burroughs\n| \"[[When She Loved Me]]\"\n| ''[[Toy Story 2]]''\n| style=\"background:#FDFC8F;\"| Safe\n|-\n| 8\n| Madison VanDenburg\n| \"[[How Far I'll Go]]\"\n| ''[[Moana (2016 film)|Moana]]''\n| style=\"background:#FDFC8F;\"| Safe\n|-\n| 9\n| [[Laine Hardy]]\n| \"[[Robin Hood (1973 film)|Oo-De-Lally]]\"\n| ''[[Robin Hood (1973 film)|Robin Hood]]''\n| style=\"background:#FDFC8F;\"| Safe\n|-\n| 10\n| [[Jeremiah Lloyd Harmon]]\n| \"[[Candle on the Water]]\"\n| ''[[Pete's Dragon (1977 film)|Pete's Dragon]]''\n| style=\"background:#FDFC8F;\"| Safe\n|-\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ Non-competition performances\n|-\n! Order\n! Performers\n! Song\n! Featured Film\n|-\n| 14.1\n| [[Lea Michele]] and the Top 10\n| \"[[Part of Your World]]\"\n| ''[[The Little Mermaid (1989 film)|The Little Mermaid]]''\n|-\n| 14.2\n| [[Maddie Poppe]] and [[Caleb Lee Hutchinson]]\n| \"[[A Whole New World]]\"\n| ''[[Aladdin (1992 Disney film)|Aladdin]]''\n|-\n|}\n\n===Week 2: Top 8 \u2013 Queen Night / Movie Duets (April 28)===\n[[Adam Lambert]] served as a guest mentor, and all the top eight members sang  [[Queen (band)|Queen]] songs. All eight remaining contestants also paired as a duet and sang songs from a movie soundtrack.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/music/news/adam-lambert-queen-returns-american-idol-mentor-1203193825/ |title=Archived copy |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420001150/https://variety.com/2019/music/news/adam-lambert-queen-returns-american-idol-mentor-1203193825/ |archive-date=2019-04-20 |access-date=2019-04-20}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:cent