r.com/live7-weekly-ratings-the-orville-on-fox-leads-broadcast-network-telecasts-in-percentage-gains-among-adults-18-49/ |title=Live+7 Weekly Ratings: \u2018The Orville\u2019 on Fox Leads Broadcast Network Telecasts in Percentage Gains Among Adults 18-49 |last=Pucci |first=Douglas |date=April 2, 2019 |website=Programming Insider |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403065441/https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-the-orville-on-fox-leads-broadcast-network-telecasts-in-percentage-gains-among-adults-18-49/ |archive-date=April 3, 2019 |access-date=April 4, 2019}}</ref>\n\n| title7     = Hollywood Week, Part 2\n| date7      = March 25, 2019\n| timeslot7  = Monday 8:00 p.m.\n| rs7        = 1.2/5\n| viewers7   = 6.45<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/monday-final-ratings-march-25-2019/ |title='The Voice,\u2019 American Idol,\u2019 \u2018The Neighborhood,\u2019 all others hold: Monday final ratings |last=Rejent |first=Joseph |date=March 26, 2019 |website=TV by the Numbers |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190326213928/https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/monday-final-ratings-march-25-2019/ |archive-date=March 26, 2019 |access-date=March 26, 2019}}</ref>\n| dvr7       = 0.4\n| dvrv7      = 1.85\n| total7     = 1.6\n| totalv7    = 8.31<ref name=\"DVR 7, 8\">{{Cite web |url=https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-greys-anatomy-silent-all-these-years-episode-on-abc-runner-up-among-broadcast-network-telecasts-in-adults-18-49-raw-gains/ |title=Live+7 Weekly Ratings: \u2018Grey\u2019s Anatomy: Silent All These Years\u2019 Episode on ABC Runner-Up Among Broadcast Network Telecasts in Adults 18-49 Raw Gains |last=Pucci |first=Douglas |date=April 9, 2019 |website=Programming Insider |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410133307/https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-greys-anatomy-silent-all-these-years-episode-on-abc-runner-